#Stayhomestaysafe Building memories one day at a time... Lookin’ fwd to the day the world be safe for her to head out to play again. For now, we’re juz staying in, glamping in & glamming up our nails with @nodspark twinning sticker nail sets. Super easy to stick on! File & Voilà.
